{"tid":2337001,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中國去年逾千萬人移民 主要去美日加三國","createTime":"2020-12-23T04:27:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T04:36:35.000Z","uid":291865,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3d4cd345b17179242bc6e8a27514bcc3532ebe6b","tid":2337001,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T04:27:55.000Z","msg":"中國去年逾千萬人移民 主要去美日加三國<br />\n<br />\n#兩岸國際 內地社會科學文獻出版社發表中國國際移民報告，最熱門國家分別是美國、日本及加拿大。 (12/23/12:14) 全文 (<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=417647\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D417647&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVp63e3GGuF%2FCnRpDBLK0zENU%3D&h=65b6201a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D417647&h=2005b338\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=417647</a>)"},{"pid":"2b4ef792d9c4db5e664e2a1463d74da9986350ea","tid":2337001,"uid":291865,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T04:28:25.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】內地社會科學文獻出版社發表中國國際移民報告，最熱門國家分別是美國、日本及加拿大。<br />\n<br />\n報告引用去年聯合國經濟和社會事務部的數據，中國大約有1073萬人移民，成為世界第三大移民輸出國。<br />\n<br />\n中國移民目的地首三位是美國、日本及加拿大，中國亦是美國與英國最大的留學生來源國，2018-19學年，美國的中國留學生佔國際學生總數三成三，學生亦有年輕化的趨勢，近十年赴美就讀高中的中國學生就增長了98倍。<br />\n<br />\n報告指疫情下各國採取封關措施，預料國際移民數目將明顯減少。"},{"pid":"c851a6c5df3bc1de83d97705f19db9c190e7e5fd","tid":2337001,"uid":40763,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T04:34:05.000Z","msg":"每一隻支那狗都係癌細胞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54dbf20a611f47eb11391df1c6b6b68b55de3cb2","tid":2337001,"uid":368884,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T04:35:55.000Z","msg":"去日本<br />\n漢奸走狗賣國賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif